Mar 2024 08:20:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-taobao-working-with-startup-deliveries-by-reusable-rocket-2024-03-31/</guid></item><item><title>首席执行官表示，斯沃琪中国买家对更高的价格犹豫不决</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/swatch-buyers-china-hesitate-over-higher-prices-ceo-says-2024-03-31/</link><description>瑞士钟表制造商斯沃琪集团首席执行官在接受报纸采访时表示，由于消费者对更高的价格犹豫不决，中国市场在今年年底前可能会遇到困难。</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 07:52:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/swatch-buyers-china-hesitate-over-higher-prices-ceo-says-2024-03-31/</guid></item><item><title>意大利人享受水手队的冲突，菲尼克斯达到季前赛目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/italiano-relishing-mariners-clash-phoenix-hit-pre-season-target-2024-03-31/</link><description>周日，惠灵顿凤凰队主教练吉安卡洛·意大利人看到他的球队实现了季前赛目标，与最接近的对手中央海岸水手队拉开了六分的差距，距离澳超联赛前两名将在一场决定赛季的冲突中相遇还不到一周。</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 07:20:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/italiano-relishing-mariners-clash-phoenix-hit-pre-season-target-2024-03-31/</guid></item><item><title>日本当局在死亡事件后检查小林制药第二家工厂</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/second-kobayashi-pharma-japan-factory-inspected-over-deaths-2024-03-31/</link><description>小林制药表示，它在去年 4 月至 10 月大阪工厂生产的 Beni-Koji 材料中发现了似乎具有潜在毒性的青春酸，这种物质可能是由蓝霉青霉产生的。</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 07:08:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/second-kobayashi-pharma-japan-factory-inspected-over-deaths-2024-03-31/</guid></item><item><title>随着中国紧张局势升级，菲律宾加强海上安全</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-marcos-boosts-maritime-security-china-tension-rises-2024-03-31/</link><description>随着与中国的争端升级，菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯下令政府加强海上安全协调，应对领土完整与和平的“一系列严重挑战”。</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 04:36:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-marcos-boosts-maritime-security-china-tension-rises-2024-03-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国3月份工厂活动六个月来首次扩张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-march-factory-activity-expands-first-time-six-months-2024-03-31/</link><description>周日的官方工厂调查显示，中国制造业活动在 3 月份出现六个月来的首次扩张，这让政策制定者松了一口气，尽管房地产行业的危机仍然拖累经济和信心。</description><pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 03:51:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-march-factory-activity-expands-first-time-six-months-2024-03-31/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯央行通过货币互换操作发放更多人民币贷款</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/russian-central-bank-lends-more-chinese-yuan-under-currency-swap-operations-2024-03-30/</link><description>俄罗斯央行表示，周五已根据货币互换交易向各银行提供了 25 亿元人民币（约合 3.4625 亿美元），相当于 318 亿卢布。</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 13:01:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/russian-central-bank-lends-more-chinese-yuan-under-currency-swap-operations-2024-03-30/</guid></item><item><title>飓风队在超级太平洋橄榄球赛中前进，十字军队获得首场胜利</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/crusaders-bag-first-win-hurricanes-march-super-rugby-pacific-2024-03-30/</link><description>周六，惠灵顿飓风队以六连胜继续其超级太平洋橄榄球赛季的完美开局，而坎特伯雷十字军队则取得了本赛季的首场胜利，将卫冕冠军从积分榜上移开。</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 11:04:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/crusaders-bag-first-win-hurricanes-march-super-rugby-pacific-2024-03-30/</guid></item><item><title>日经新闻称，日本和欧盟将讨论技术材料合作，以减少对中国的依赖</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/japan-eu-discuss-cooperation-tech-materials-cut-reliance-china-nikkei-says-2024-03-30/</link><description>据《日经新闻》周六报道，日本和欧盟计划开始讨论在下一代芯片和电池的先进材料方面进行合作，以减少对中国的依赖。</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 09:17:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/japan-eu-discuss-cooperation-tech-materials-cut-reliance-china-nikkei-says-2024-03-30/</guid></item><item><title>伊兰昆达创造帽子戏法新纪录后，维尔特呼吁保持耐心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/veart-calls-patience-after-irankunda-sets-new-hat-trick-record-2024-03-30/</link><description>阿德莱德联队主教练卡尔·维尔特敦促澳大利亚球迷对新晋天才内斯托里·伊兰昆达保持耐心，因为这名即将前往拜仁慕尼黑的前锋成为澳大利亚联赛有史以来最年轻的帽子戏法球员。</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 07:23:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/veart-calls-patience-after-irankunda-sets-new-hat-trick-record-2024-03-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国开发商万达以83亿美元的交易出售购物中心60%的股份</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-developer-wanda-sells-60-mall-unit-83-bln-deal-2024-03-30/</link><description>周六，以私募股权公司 PAG 为首的一群投资者宣布投资 83 亿美元，收购中国房地产巨头大连万达旗下购物中心部门 60% 的股份。</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 06:32:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/china-developer-wanda-sells-60-mall-unit-83-bln-deal-2024-03-30/</guid></item><item><title>华为表示奇瑞豪华S7豪华电动汽车开始批量交付</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/huawei-says-cherys-luxeed-s7-premium-ev-starts-mass-delivery-2024-03-30/</link><description>华为高管周六表示，由中国科技巨头华为和奇瑞汽车开发的 Luxeed S7 电动轿车在半导体短缺和生产问题推迟生产和交付后已开始批量交付。</description><pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 04:48:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/huawei-says-cherys-luxeed-s7-premium-ev-starts-mass-delivery-2024-03-30/</guid></item></channel></rss>